.fc-cal-day-candy {
  background-color: rgb(52, 52, 52);
  color: rgb(204, 204, 204);
  font-family: "Fira Sans Light";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-date-normal-candy {
  background-color: rgb(52, 52, 52);
  color: rgb(204, 204, 204);
  font-family: "Fira Sans Light";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-date-normal-candy:hover {
  background-color: rgb(110, 110, 110);
  color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
  font-family: "Fira Sans Light";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-date-disabled-candy {
  background-color: rgb(52, 52, 52);
  color: rgba(153, 156, 165, 0.75);
  font-family: "Fira Sans Light";
  border: none;
}

.fc-cal-month-header-candy {
  background-color: rgb(54, 134, 156);
  font-family: "Fira Sans Light";
}

.fc-cal-weekend-candy {
  background-color: rgb(53, 85, 93);
}

.fc-cal-container-candy {
  border: 0.5px solid rgb(75, 75, 75);
}
